Entmoot includes an independent Go implementation of the Pilot Protocol
IPC wire format, written from the public specification at
https://github.com/TeoSlayer/pilotprotocol/blob/main/docs/SPEC.md.
It does not incorporate code from the Pilot Protocol reference
implementation.
